# Treat image/binary assets as binary so they are never passed through
# text/line-ending normalization (which previously corrupted public/kanto.png,
# turning the PNG header byte 0x89 into the UTF-8 replacement sequence EF BF BD).
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.webp binary
*.ico  binary
*.mp3  binary
*.flac binary
*.wav  binary
*.ogg  binary
